        {"type":0,"content":"3/25/26 \\n\\nYesterday: Made some general improvements on the Journal Screen UI and the Home Screen UI. Added Gemeni AI to the rubber duck debugger. Added voice recognition tools to the debugger. Encountered some errors in the work I did. \\n\\nToday: I'll be real honest, I took the day off. I did some guitar repair work for a friends made some extra cash. Had the day off from work. My son is on spring break right now so me and him went and had a picnic at the park, then I bought him a toy from marshalls. Came home and played some pokemon with him. About to make some dinner and get us ready for bed time afterwards. \\n\\nTomorrow: Try to work out some of the problems I have in my code and get a functioning prototype debugger available for the class to take over from there. \\n\\nBlockers: The issues I'm experiencing with the voice recognition might be tied to android studio emulators, may need to hook up a phone to the IDE but my phone's USB port is absololutely busted, so trying to do more research before I find an alternative.","mentions":[],"mention_roles":[],"attachments":[],"embeds":[],"timestamp":"2026-03-26T00:41:47.632000+00:00","edited_timestamp":null,"flags":0,"components":[],"id":"1486525542462132398","channel_id":"1478078339632730223","author":{"id":"790404319957876789","username":"pervysagekip","avatar":"850df8641933da68e7dec607147c725a","discriminator":"0","public_flags":0,"flags":0,"banner":null,"accent_color":null,"global_name":"PervySageKip","avatar_decoration_data":null,"collectibles":null,"display_name_styles":null,"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"pinned":false,"mention_everyone":false,"tts":false,"reactions":[{"emoji":{"id":null,"name":"\\ud83e\\udd23"},"count":1,"count_details":{"burst":0,"normal":1},"burst_colors":[],"me_burst":false,"burst_me":false,"me":false,"burst_count":0}]}
