        {"type":0,"content":"3/24/26 \\n\\nYesterday: Started the framework for AsyncStorage and Journal Entry UI and the Home Screen integration. Meaning I want Recent Journal Entries displayed on the Home Screen, I want the entries to be pressable and editable. Had to add cancel buttons to the Journal Entries when the user is making a new entry and navigation on when that happens to take them back to the Journal Screen. \\n\\nToday: Made some more integration on the Journal Entries UI and the home screen integration, encountered some logic issues where the screens don't want to navigate as intended. Added a gemini agent to the Rubber Duck mode so that the user can connect to a gemini agent as a debugger assistant. Attempted to add speech to text so that the user can talk to the agent but encountered some errors getting the app to connect to the mic. \\n\\nTomorrow: Fiddle with the code base to work out the logic errors I'm experiencing.\\n\\nBlockers: The waters get muddy real fast, logic errors (The Code I made isn't working as intended) \\nHave to spend some time analyzing where it's going wrong.","mentions":[],"mention_roles":[],"attachments":[],"embeds":[],"timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:26:45.985000+00:00","edited_timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:28:30.607000+00:00","flags":0,"components":[],"id":"1486053676354375681","channel_id":"1478078339632730223","author":{"id":"790404319957876789","username":"pervysagekip","avatar":"850df8641933da68e7dec607147c725a","discriminator":"0","public_flags":0,"flags":0,"banner":null,"accent_color":null,"global_name":"PervySageKip","avatar_decoration_data":null,"collectibles":null,"display_name_styles":null,"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"pinned":false,"mention_everyone":false,"tts":false}
