        {"type":0,"content":"Date: 3/23/2026 \\n\\nYesterday: Did more research into how multipage app projects are usually set up to get more familiar with the project structure as well as research into the different ways to code user interactions into an app. \\n\\nToday/Tomorrow: Started looking into how to implement a \\u201cslider bar\\u201d choice selection to allow users to select a stress level within the mood page of the app. Also pulled dev to get the most recent version of the project and ensure I had everything installed to get the app to run correctly, then merged dev into my branch so I could start working with the updated version of the project. For tomorrow, I\\u2019m going to begin work on getting a functional slider bar then customize the bar to fit the project and after that attempt to get specific text to display based on the user\\u2019s selection. \\n\\nBlockers: Tried to pull dev through visual studio but kept running into an error relating to the files created by visual studio. I was able to successfully pull the dev branch through using the GitHub desktop app.","mentions":[],"mention_roles":[],"attachments":[],"embeds":[],"timestamp":"2026-03-24T02:57:00.445000+00:00","edited_timestamp":null,"flags":0,"components":[],"id":"1485834794335207636","channel_id":"1478078339632730223","author":{"id":"1390831788905074759","username":"chay_lars","avatar":"cd435ba634eb65a90f37a93ebb396468","discriminator":"0","public_flags":0,"flags":0,"banner":null,"accent_color":null,"global_name":null,"avatar_decoration_data":null,"collectibles":null,"display_name_styles":null,"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"pinned":false,"mention_everyone":false,"tts":false}
