        {"type":0,"content":"3/22/26 \\n\\nYesterday: Started on screen navigation and made placeholder screens for each feature. \\n\\nToday: Expanded on the screen and began to implement AsyncStorage so that Journal Entries can be done locally. \\n\\nTomorrow: Work on expanding the Journal Entries to allow for pushable cards that lead to modal screens of past Journal Entries and allow for them to be edited. \\n\\nBlockers: After installing AsyncStorage onto my device I was experiencing some weird problems where the app would crash everytime I tried to load it. Stuck in debugging that.","mentions":[],"mention_roles":[],"attachments":[],"embeds":[],"timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:44:48.345000+00:00","edited_timestamp":null,"flags":0,"components":[],"id":"1485439136830853261","channel_id":"1478078339632730223","author":{"id":"790404319957876789","username":"pervysagekip","avatar":"850df8641933da68e7dec607147c725a","discriminator":"0","public_flags":0,"flags":0,"banner":null,"accent_color":null,"global_name":"PervySageKip","avatar_decoration_data":null,"collectibles":null,"display_name_styles":null,"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"pinned":false,"mention_everyone":false,"tts":false}
