        {"type":0,"content":"3/21/26 \\n\\nYesterday: Had to go through some debugging to correct my files, dependencies and file paths to get the project running in android studio. \\n\\nToday: coded out screen navigation including bottom tab navigation with some placeholder ui design on each screen. Recorded a video going through the changes I made to show the team before pushing to the repo. \\n\\nTomorrow: make sure all my code is pushed to the repo and start researching more of the logic necessary for each screen. Research async storage so the app can save jsons or other files locally so that the app can function closer to the design idea. \\n\\nBlockers: none for now.","mentions":[],"mention_roles":[],"attachments":[],"embeds":[],"timestamp":"2026-03-22T13:22:11.036000+00:00","edited_timestamp":null,"flags":0,"components":[],"id":"1485267349425881253","channel_id":"1478078339632730223","author":{"id":"790404319957876789","username":"pervysagekip","avatar":"850df8641933da68e7dec607147c725a","discriminator":"0","public_flags":0,"flags":0,"banner":null,"accent_color":null,"global_name":"PervySageKip","avatar_decoration_data":null,"collectibles":null,"display_name_styles":null,"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"pinned":false,"mention_everyone":false,"tts":false}
