        {"type":0,"content":"Date: 3/21/2026 \\n\\nYesterday: Testing myself on learning Kotlin. Started to write light pseudo code for the layout of the pages. Completed translatable pseudocode for the Title screen.\\n\\nToday/Tomorrow: Completed pseudocode for the Dashboard (zero state). Started to learn beginner/intermediate JS language along with my beginner knowledge of Kotlin, replaced items of pseudocode with my current knowledge of both languages. Began cross-referencing JS, Kotlin, and React Native docs to map pseudocode to real implementation. Started researching into TypeScript and React docs to determine what will be needed for the screens. Tomorrow I will further investigate where I can be utilized if even just to refine the figma screens while I learn more about how to code. Added the pseudocode to the repo under docs.\\n\\nBlockers: I am new to nearly all of the languages, frameworks and systems we are using, I need to do more research on what we need and how to implement those things, rather than learning for mastery. Identified that full screen builds should come after stronger language footing.","mentions":[],"mention_roles":[],"attachments":[],"embeds":[],"timestamp":"2026-03-21T22:18:07.572000+00:00","edited_timestamp":"2026-03-22T17:24:24.392000+00:00","flags":0,"components":[],"id":"1485039835847594035","channel_id":"1478078339632730223","author":{"id":"641164687261827086","username":"semidigitalvirgo","avatar":"92cc071a6156b6eaacbadcf2cbb1a901","discriminator":"0","public_flags":0,"flags":0,"banner":null,"accent_color":null,"global_name":"Ceecee","avatar_decoration_data":null,"collectibles":null,"display_name_styles":null,"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"pinned":false,"mention_everyone":false,"tts":false}
