        {"type":0,"content":"Date: 3/20/2026\\n\\nYesterday:\\nI focused on getting the React Native project running correctly on my local machine and was able to successfully run the app on my personal branch. I also synced my branch with the dev branch and resolved merge conflicts so my local environment is now up to date with the team\\u2019s progress.\\n\\nToday/Tomorrow:\\nI plan to begin working on improving the login flow. My goal is to implement basic functionality so that signing up stores user credentials securely and logging in routes the user to the home reflection screen. I will also research backend options such as Supabase or Firebase for handling authentication and future data storage.\\n\\nBlockers:\\nI am still becoming more comfortable with Git workflows and resolving merge conflicts, but I was able to work through the issues","mentions":[],"mention_roles":[],"attachments":[],"embeds":[],"timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:00:59.076000+00:00","edited_timestamp":null,"flags":0,"components":[],"id":"1484778830618034247","channel_id":"1478078339632730223","author":{"id":"1008114177241526372","username":"b2thejamin","avatar":"4a183021b9430ed5764aad07f0580d75","discriminator":"0","public_flags":0,"flags":0,"banner":null,"accent_color":null,"global_name":"bjamin","avatar_decoration_data":null,"collectibles":null,"display_name_styles":{"font_id":7,"effect_id":2,"colors":[16718080,16738816]},"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"pinned":false,"mention_everyone":false,"tts":false}
