        {"type":0,"content":"Date: 3/20/2026 \\n\\nYesterday: Created a basic layout for a log-in page using text, text input boxes, and buttons then after the zoom session, pushed the code to my branch for the rest of the team to use as foundation for the project \\n\\nToday/Tomorrow: I did some more research into react native and how to interact with text input from users since that seems like that aspect would be something important for a journaling app and started looking into coding using Kotlin in case the team does decide to fully use Kotlin for the project. For what comes, probably team discussions about what different screens and aspects to start tackling for the project \\n\\nBlockers: It seemed like there were some issues with attempting to merge the branches, but the instructor helped resolve those and it looks like most of the team was able to get the project into a runnable state after the many errors everyone ran into when trying to begin the project","mentions":[],"mention_roles":[],"attachments":[],"embeds":[],"timestamp":"2026-03-21T03:30:47.618000+00:00","edited_timestamp":null,"flags":0,"components":[],"id":"1484756133318103080","channel_id":"1478078339632730223","author":{"id":"1390831788905074759","username":"chay_lars","avatar":"cd435ba634eb65a90f37a93ebb396468","discriminator":"0","public_flags":0,"flags":0,"banner":null,"accent_color":null,"global_name":null,"avatar_decoration_data":null,"collectibles":null,"display_name_styles":null,"banner_color":null,"clan":null,"primary_guild":null},"pinned":false,"mention_everyone":false,"tts":false}
